						               													<description>Portable lunchbox game. The Marvel Heroes are always equipped and ready to go and now you can follow suit. Have great time wherever your adventures take you. Heroes unite. Players 2-4.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Product Features&amp;#10;The Marvel Heroes are always equipped and ready to go and now you can follow suit&amp;#10;Have great time wherever your adventures take you&amp;#10;Heroes unite&amp;#10;For Ages 4+&amp;#10;Players 2-4&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players roll dice on their turns in order to match the superhero icons on the dice to the villains currently at large on the table. To capture a villain such as the Lizard requires one Spiderman icon. To capture Galactus requires one each of Captain America, Hulk and Spiderman. Players may reroll &amp;quot;misses&amp;quot; but once an &amp;quot;X&amp;quot; is rolled, that die cannot be rerolled so there is a slight press-your-luck element.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are some wild cards that give players an icon of their choice. Some other special cards give players extra rerolls or force a player to give up one of their previously captured villains.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The winner is the player who has captured the most villains when the deck runs out.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
